_header: O ye holy angels in your orders nine
Subjects: prayers, to guardian angel; prayers, to saints
_description: A prayer to all angels and saints — one stanza rhyme royal

Bod549.First Lines:
O ȝe holy Angeles in ȝour Ordres nynePatriarkes Prophetes
                    and Apostoles alle…
Bod549.Last Lines:
…Comfessours and virgines putteth to ȝour handeHelpeth
                    alle cristen in speciall Ingeland
